@matthiasblaesing have added your commit (removed an unused import)

> @DevCharly an option in FlatLaf to prefer trying to load via System::loadLibrary without full path would be great in future!

I wonder where Java/NetBeans searches for libraries if System::loadLibrary is used?

@mbien thanks for checking in and confirming my suspicion
@neilcsmith-net Thanks for the check. I verified the right code path by using a debugger and stepping through `c.s.j.Native#loadNativeDispatchLibrary`. The right codepath was taken (after, before I have verified that the wrong was taken).

For changes to the loading in JNA im reluctant. It took long to make the change and until now, no one raised an issue.
